[laughs, gasps]

265
00:14:48,541 --> 00:14:49,791
Score one for the old guy.

266
00:14:49,875 --> 00:14:51,291
[grunts]

267
00:14:52,333 --> 00:14:53,250
[clicks]

268
00:14:54,416 --> 00:14:55,250
