--[beeps]

329
00:18:41,875 --> 00:18:43,291
[CROWD screaming]

330
00:18:46,375 --> 00:18:47,625
[gasps]

331
00:18:47,708 --> 00:18:49,833
--[rock music playing]
--[gasps]

332
00:18:55,041 --> 00:18:56,500
[CROWD] Huh?

333
00:18:56,583 --> 00:18:59,041
[gasps]

334
00:18:59,125 --> 00:19:00,833
Isn't that Ma-bo from Momi-Ham?

335
00:19:00,916 --> 00:19:02,416
Han-can's there, too!

336
00:19:09,375 --> 00:19:11,250
[grunts, gasps]

337
00:19:17,166 --> 00:19:18,125
[gasps]

338
00:19:19,208 --> 00:19:20,333
[MAMECHIYO] Misa.

339
00:19:28,458 --> 00:19:30,375
[music stops]

340
00:19:30,458 --> 00:19:32,375
Uh... [sighs]

341
00:19:32,458 --> 00:19:33,666
[CROWD] Huh?

342
00:19:38,291 --> 00:19:39,666
[gasps]

343
00:19:56,666 --> 00:19:57,916
Hey, is that...?

344
00:19:58,000 --> 00:20:00,125
Looks like Momizo.

345
00:20:00,208 --> 00:20:03,125
It looks like him, but...

346
00:20:05,458 --> 00:20:07,166
[CROWD]
He's gotten fat!

347
00:20:08,875 --> 00:20:10,666
--[MAMECHIYO] Over here, Misa!
--[gasps]

348
00:20:12,375 --> 00:20:13,833
[MISA]
Is that Chiyo?

349
00:20:15,375 --> 00:20:18,708
Misa, I'm-- I'm so sorry!

350
00:20:21,458 --> 00:20:22,416
[grunts]

351
00:20:27,666 --> 00:20:31,208
Huh. [grunts, shouts]

352
00:20:33,416 --> 00:20:36,375
I hope you forgive me, Chiyo!
I'm sorry, too!

353
00:20:44,208 --> 00:20:46,041
[BOTH gasp]

354
00:20:47,083 --> 00:20:48,666
Han-chan, count us off.

